steps.name: Login with Audit Manager credentials in Login page
Click on WovenKnit Module
Click on Audit Module
Click on Pending IPO list in menu
Verify whether user navigated to Pending IPO list or not
Verify whether the data is displaying in grid or not
Click on Generate IPO button
Verify whether Generate IPO screen is displaying or not
Verify whether the current date is displaying for IPO date field or not
verify whether the Buyer Style is prepopulated or not
Verify whether the IPO field is prepopulated with data or not
Enter IPO number in IPO field
Insert and select Production Merchant
Verify the PO qty is prepopulated or not
Enter IPO qty in text field
Select Assigned Month Year
verify whether the exfactory is prepopulated or not
Disable the Active checkbox
Click on cancel button
Click the Save button
